{"tid":135193,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲打用緊CMHK嘅Plan?","createTime":"2017-02-26T07:25:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T12:01:44.000Z","uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d6e08bfcb302db788d158e246b8e437a0f3c8f","tid":135193,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:25:45.000Z","msg":"小弟因為窮所以焗住用佢$68個plan<br />\n有無人知呢間濕柒公司今日做乜撚嘢？<br />\n你地有冇咁嘅情況<br />\n咁事源今日我就出街啦<br />\n我就要由深水埗站搭去九龍塘站<br />\n一上咗架地鐵個on9 CMHK就嚟料啦<br />\n由4G跌到落3G,跟住就開始無晒信號<br />\n直到我係九龍塘出咗閘,係出面行咗一段時間(大約20分鐘)<br />\n先回復返「3G」嘅信號比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我打去佢地客戶服務熱線(29458888)問啦,竟然可以無法通話<br />\n我真係屌你老母呀,大大個hotline放係自己個網頁度竟然打唔撚到<br />\n打唔到你整係到托柒呀？平時要交電話費、想人續約嘅時候又唔見你打唔通<br />\n仲要好撚似催命符咁係撚咁打嚟,屌你老母<br />\n用佢地網頁嘅live chat功能問又要排隊<br />\n想log ln問又send唔到password比我log in<br />\n仆街啦你,咁嘅服務質素仲學人加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我祝你公社全體仝人陷家長命百歲,百病纏身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac3bf4da5cc041a9c337785cd0a4e5002b973f5","tid":135193,"uid":10520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8035c5f6727fac97473d0f4733c80ea2855b767c","tid":135193,"uid":2629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"無是咁的，0分重作"},{"pid":"e85536b40800011b2b70ab3e54ea308c01b40699","tid":135193,"uid":66283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:30:21.000Z","msg":"今日係收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，電話都打唔到"},{"pid":"e1fc7b6939adf4c2de9b7ea4daa40040dd098862","tid":135193,"uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:34:45.000Z","msg":"我都係，以為自己問題"},{"pid":"7aa4e8acb74323a314b0a2c023d9fc3b6e2b5242","tid":135193,"uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":